# ── Create ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a cave (no auth required for POST — or protect it as needed)
POST {{api}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}

{
  "name": "Bystrianska Cave",
  "public_payload": {
    "kind": "cave",
    "region": "Slovakia",
    "tags": ["karst", "tourism"],
    "protected": true
  },
  "caver_payload": {
    "length_m": 2900,
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "entrance_gps": [48.847, 19.064],
    "equipment_required": ["helmet", "lamp"]
  },
  "scientific_payload": {
    "geology": "mesozoic limestone",
    "discovered": 1968,
    "species_count": 14,
    "secret": "bystrianska-classified"
  }
}


# ── List all events (role determines visible fields) ──────────────────────────

### List as basic user  →  public_payload only
GET {{api}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCharlie}}

### List as caver  →  public_payload + caver_payload
GET {{api}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAlice}}

### List as researcher  →  all three payloads
GET {{api}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenBob}}

### List as admin  →  all three payloads
GET {{api}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}


# ── Filter by kind ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Filter by kind=cave (as caver)
GET {{api}}/events/by-kind/cave
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAlice}}


# ── Filter by length ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Caves longer than 1000 m (as researcher)
GET {{api}}/events/longer-than/1000
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenBob}}


# ── Advanced filter ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Filter: cave + Slovakia + protected (as caver)
GET {{api}}/events/filter?kind=cave&region=Slovakia&protected=true
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAlice}}

### Filter: min_length=800 + max_length=3000 (as researcher)
GET {{api}}/events/filter?min_length=800&max_length=3000
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenBob}}


# ── Health ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{api}}/health
